Changes to the Privacy Notice
We will regularly review and update this Notice, so we encourage you to review it periodically. If we change our privacy notice in a way that significantly changes how we process the personal information we hold about you, we will alert you to material changes by placing a notice on our websites, or by sending you an email (if you have registered your e-mail details with us).
Any significant changes in processing will come in to force no sooner than thirty (30) days after notification through this Notice.